{
  "stem": "27390.8",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And we landed in a place, in Carlisle, I think was, nearby the airport.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And from there we were put on coaches and taken to the lake district, [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And we were put into little huts.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "It was a-- the war-- it was-- there was an aircraft factory, and the workers lived in these little huts.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And it had a-- it contained a bunk and a little wardrobe and a small table with a chair.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "But to us, this was paradise.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And then we started getting food.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "We came-- they had a big dining hall where we all went into to eat.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I must say the British government gave permission to bring over thousand boys, and-- but they couldn't find thousand boys.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "They only managed to get together 750 or 740.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "They searched over all of Germany and Czechoslovakia, and they couldn't find thousand boys.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Because the boys my age and younger were all killed off.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "So anyway, we-- we-- we started eating.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "They bring in bread and butter and porridge in the morning.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "We got porridge.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And the bread kept disappearing from the tables.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And the people that were feeding us, they couldn't understand.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "They're bringing in hundreds and hundreds of loaves of bread, and it's all disappearing.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "Because we were so we used to hide food, we couldn't believe that there would ever be a time when we would have enough food.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "So we used to hide the food under the table, and we used to carry it into our rooms and hide it in the rooms.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "That went on for about a week or two weeks until finally the bread was moldy, and we realized there's no need for it.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "We would get plenty of it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "So we stopped doing that.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
